Greece’s Rating Lowered to CC by Standard & Poor’s With Negative Outlook

-- B y   G r e g   C h a n g
-- 
2011-07-27T16:37:45Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-07-27/greece-s-rating-lowered-to-cc-by-standard-poor-s-with-negative-outlook.html
Greece  had its debt rating cut to CC
from CCC by  Standard & Poor’s , which said a proposed
restructuring would amount to a “selective default.”  The debt exchange in the proposal would result in losses
for commercial creditors, S&P said. The outlook on the rating is
negative.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Greg Chang at 
 gchang1@bloomberg.net  